parameters.name: SCET_UTC
parameters.description: Sample S/C event time UTC in YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sss format

parameters.name: AOBT
parameters.description:
APSS onboard time (AOBT) value of sample. This is the spacecraft
                        clock time used by the APSS instruments.

parameters.name: MLST
parameters.description:
Mars local solar time (hh:mm:ss) converts Sun angle 
                       to 24 hour clock.

parameters.name: conf
parameters.description:
Configuration table number used to define onboard
                       processing including IFG down-sampling rate and the
                       computation of the estimated parameters.

parameters.name: off
parameters.description: Sample offset within the downlink packet (samples 0 - 1023).

parameters.name: IFG1_DN
parameters.description: IFG axis 1 value in data numbers.

parameters.name: IFG2_DN
parameters.description: IFG axis 2 value in data numbers.

parameters.name: IFG3_DN
parameters.description: IFG axis 3 value in data numbers.

parameters.name: IFGT_DN
parameters.description: IFG sensor temperature value in data numbers.

parameters.name: PAE_T
parameters.description:
PAE temperature (T-0014) in deg C used to estimate electronics 
                       temperature. This temperature is measured on the electronics 
                       box that houses the IFG components but is not the value from
                       the thermister on the board that is required for the temperature
                       calibrations (sensor gains and zero levels).
